@inject IJSRuntime JSRuntime
@using SaveFW.Client.Pages

<section class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0B1221] py-24 relative overflow-hidden" id="mayor-critique">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Policy Critique</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
                THE "ARSONIST FIREFIGHTER" <span class="text-orange-600">MODEL</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-xl italic text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                "An arsonist who starts a fire just so they can be paid to put it out."
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-16">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 cursor-pointer group"
                    onclick="window.openImageModal('assets/MAYOR_SHARON_TUCKER_AND_SENATOR_JUSTIN_BUSCH_ARSONIST_FIREFIGHTERS_COMIC.png')">
                    <img src="assets/MAYOR_SHARON_TUCKER_AND_SENATOR_JUSTIN_BUSCH_ARSONIST_FIREFIGHTERS_COMIC.png"
                        alt="Comic strip"
                        class="w-full h-auto block transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" />
                </div>
                <p class="text-center italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium px-4">
                    State Senator Justin Busch and Mayor Sharon Tucker pouring gasoline onto the fire that is the
                    city's homelessness crisis.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
                <p>
                    Mayor Sharon Tucker and State Senator Justin Busch argue that we need casino revenue to fund the
                    "Humanitarian Fund" for the homeless. But this ignores a basic reality: casinos are a leading
                    cause of the financial ruin that leads to homelessness.
                </p>
                <p class="font-bold">
                    A policy that relies on creating new victims to fund services for existing ones
                    isn't a solutionâ€”it is a Ponzi scheme of human misery.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FULL DECODING THE SPIN SECTION -->
        <div class="mt-24 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pt-12">
            <div class="mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
                    Decoding the <span class="text-orange-600">Spin</span>
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-center mb-12">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-2">
                        Phrases taken directly from <strong><a href="https://fwfirst.com/" target="_blank"
                                class="underline hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">FWFirst's</a></strong>
                        marketing materials and Mayor Tucker's press releases.
                    </p>
                    <span class="block text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
                        Note: Since the website's content may change, SaveFW has <a
                            href="https://web.archive.org/web/20251224153405/https://fwfirst.com/" target="_blank"
                            class="underline hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">archived a copy of FWFirst's
                            website</a> as of December 24, 2025.
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-12">
                <!-- Category 1: Economic Engine -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-orange-500">trending_down</span>
                        "Economic Engine" Myth
                    </h4>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Pitch</span>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">ECONOMIC ENGINE</li>
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
                                Promises of growth often ignore the displacement of existing spending.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Reality</span>
                            <details class="group bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/10 rounded-lg border border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/50 open:bg-white dark:open:bg-slate-800 open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer list-none outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:outline-none display-none-before">
                                    <span class="font-black text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 text-xs uppercase">Local Businesses Lost</span>
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-sm transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="px-3 pb-3 pt-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed border-t border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/30">
                                    The "Substitution Effect" means money is not imported; it is simply diverted from local restaurants, theaters, and retail to the casino, creating a net loss for the existing economy.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Category 2: Jobs -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-orange-500">work_off</span>
                        "Jobs" Promise
                    </h4>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Pitch</span>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">GOOD PAYING JOBS</li>
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">RETAIN TALENT</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
                                "Good jobs" that pay less than fast food?
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Reality</span>
                            <details class="group bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/10 rounded-lg border border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/50 open:bg-white dark:open:bg-slate-800 open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer list-none outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:outline-none display-none-before">
                                    <span class="font-black text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 text-xs uppercase">Low Wage Jobs</span>
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-sm transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="px-3 pb-3 pt-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed border-t border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/30">
                                    Line Cooks at Rising Star earn $13-$17/hr vs $20/hr avg at local fast food. You earn 35% more at Wendy's than at their "world-class" property.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Category 3: Community Health -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-orange-500">medical_services</span>
                        Community Health & Safety
                    </h4>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Pitch</span>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">HUMANITARIAN FUND</li>
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">COMMUNITY WELL-BEING</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
                                How can a fund fix the damage caused by the funding source?
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Reality</span>
                            <details class="group bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/10 rounded-lg border border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/50 open:bg-white dark:open:bg-slate-800 open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer list-none outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:outline-none display-none-before">
                                    <span class="font-black text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 text-xs uppercase">Addiction</span>
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-sm transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="px-3 pb-3 pt-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed border-t border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/30">
                                    96% of individuals with gambling disorder have co-occurring psychiatric disorders. The resulting addiction damages savings and family relationships.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Category 4: Destination -->
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-orange-500">public_off</span>
                        "World-Class" Destination
                    </h4>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Pitch</span>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">WORLD-CLASS DESTINATION</li>
                                <li class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/10 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 text-xs font-bold">RESPONSIBLE GAMING</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
                                "Responsible" for who? The casinos or the families?
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-3 block tracking-widest">The Reality</span>
                            <details class="group bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/10 rounded-lg border border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/50 open:bg-white dark:open:bg-slate-800 open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer list-none outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 active:outline-none display-none-before">
                                    <span class="font-black text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 text-xs uppercase">Saturation Barrier</span>
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-sm transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="px-3 pb-3 pt-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed border-t border-red-100 dark:border-red-800/30">
                                    Fort Wayne is surrounded by established competitors. Without a unique hook, it cannot pull tourists past the venues they already drive past.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>